{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986680/extras/Untitled_Artwork_8-export.png?t=1737006948\" /><br><br>Versus Purgatory is a micro-roguelike shoot-em-up with mind-bending gameplay in which you delve into a dungeon, controlling two characters at the same time.<br><br><strong>Don\u2019t let the two characters fool you, this is a single-player game!</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Shoot-em-up action!<br></li><li>Novel control scheme!<br></li><li>15 unique weapons to discover!<br></li><li>20+ power-ups!<br></li><li>Millions of possible dungeons!<br></li><li>Achievements!</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986680/extras/IMG_0346.PNG?t=1737006948\" /><br>Versus Purgatory is a <i>randomly-generated action shooter roguelike</i>. Find wild and exciting new <i>weapons and power-ups</i> that change how you play. Discover secrets and fight your way to freedom.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986680/extras/IMG_0347.PNG?t=1737006948\" /><br>Two spirits, an angel and a devil, were sentenced to Purgatory for their deviancy. Despite their hatred for one another, they must work together to <i>shoot, blast, and zap</i> their way out of the <i>ever-changing labyrinth</i> they've been trapped in.<br><br><strong>This game takes ~2-3 hours on average to beat.</strong><br><strong>Gamepad is strongly recommended!</strong>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2986680?t=1737006948","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2986680?t=1737006948","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986680/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737006948","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986680/capsule_184x69.